Package: MbioAssy2
Title: Integrated Analysis of Microbial Community Assembly
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ling", "Yuan", email = "yuanling@westlake.edu.cn", role = "aut"),
    person("Ze", "Zhao", email = "zhaoze@westlake.edu.cn", role = "aut"),
    person("Feng", "Ju", email = "jufeng@westlake.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Maintainer: Ze Zhao <zhaoze@westlake.edu.cn>
Description: Provides an integrated pipeline for assessing ecological stochasticity 
    and determinism in microbial community assembly. It includes modules for 
    Normalized Stochasticity Ratio (NST) calculation, Neutral Model analysis, 
    iCAMP null model analysis, C-score variance analysis, and Co-occurrence 
    Network construction.
URL: https://gaospecial.github.io/MbioAssy2
